DevOps is basically a movement rather than destined technological tool,it is the union of people,processes(ideation,code,C.I,C.D,monitoring)
and tools to enable continuous delivery of valuable products to end users.

There are many benefits of adopting DevOps in organisations,here are a few imp.benefits:-
Reduced Infrastructure costs.
Iterative cycles,automation tools help reduce time on manual tasks and paves way to create new functionalities.
Shorter production times.
Greater collaboration with Dev and Ops teams.
